        "media_type": "CAROUSEL_ALBUM",
        "caption": "Most sellers think kitchen prep starts with a renovation.\n\nIt doesn't. It starts with one corner.\n\nThe one where the mail piles up. Where the toaster lives. Where the stand mixer hides. Every kitchen has it.\n\nClear that one corner \u2014 completely \u2014 and you change how a buyer reads the whole home. The difference between \"someone lives here\" and \"someone cares about this place.\"\n\nIt's also the cheapest thing on the prep list.\n\nIf you're thinking about selling in Highland Park, University Park, or Preston Hollow, send me the address. I'll walk through what I'd actually clear first \u2014 and what I wouldn't touch.\n\n#DallasRealEstate #DallasRealtor #HighlandParkTX #UniversityParkTX #ParkCitiesRealEstate #PrestonHollow #DallasLuxuryHomes #MelissaMettryRealEstate #SellerPrep",
